  ("XP_FVC_SPEC_COR",
   ``!xl f P c.
      SIMPLE c
      ==>
      (!l:(string#value)list. (MAP FST l = xl) ==> (MAP FST (f l) = xl))
      ==>
      (VARS c SUBSET (set xl))
      ==>
